
Move a layer with your left mouse button pressed.
Scale a layer with your right mouse button down 
(not the final solution, because it is not properly working on touchscreens)


Besides a recent mono version you'll also need:

gtk-sharp2
librsvg2-2

On MeeGo, you don't have to install additional packages, just make
sure that MeeGo is up-to-date.

INSTALLATION:
=============

chmod +x create-database.sh
./create-database.sh // extract image files and create ComponentDB.xml
mono MeeGen.exe // you should start the app from the terminal to see exception & crash output.
